# ENTITY::GET_ENTITY_FORWARD_Y

## Summary
Gets the vehicles forward Y component

## Parameters
* **ENTITY_INDEX** entity

## Returns
* **FLOAT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Gets the Y-component of the entity's forward vector.
